15) Plot_syncom_from_multi_simulation_data_CF_SynCom21.m\
\
Plots byproduct formation by species and species biomass formation on byproducts in a consumer-producer matrix, as in main Figure 4A-F, Figure 5B-C. Compare SMINT-PARINT model to a model without SMINT-PARINT interaction using fitted parameter set for CF, death, primary resource consumption and predation. Data from 
