16) Testing_competition_SnyCom21_individual_CF.m\
\
Plot the inividual obseverd biomass in soil using the Excel file 
\f1\fs20 MergedData_copy.xlsx
\f0\fs24 . First section used to generate Figure 2C. Last section compare observed community with 20 to observed community with 21 members Figure 4B.\
