17) Transferred_Plot_SynCom.m\
\
Generates a soil microcosm community with 21 members with weekly transfer into a fresh environment. Simulations model using SMINT-PARINT interactions using fitted set is performed as well as simulation without SMINT-PARINT interactions (only resource competition). Supplementary Figure  9.\
\
